languages.text: Увы, не было меж ними понимания стиля боя друг друга. Скитарии мешали Ангелам Императора, те же случайно сокрушали воинов Омниссии своими атаками. Узрев, что победа ускользает, Оптикон-22 отдал свой последний приказ.

traits.locale_text: Увы, не было меж ними понимания стиля боя друг друга. Скитарии мешали Ангелам Императора, те же случайно сокрушали воинов Омниссии своими атаками. Узрев, что победа ускользает, Оптикон-22 отдал свой последний приказ.

languages.text: Alas, there was no understanding of each other's customs of combat. The Skitarii hindered the Emperor's Angels, and the latter destroyed the Omnissiah's warriors with careless attacks. Victory was slipping from their grasp, thus Opticon-22 issued his final order.

traits.locale_text: Alas, there was no understanding of each other's customs of combat between the two. The Skitarii were getting in the way of the Emperor's Angels, and the latter were destroying the Omnissiah's warriors with careless attacks. Victory was slipping from their grasp, so Opticon-22 gave his final order.

languages.text: 遗憾的是，这两位指挥官根本不了解彼此的战斗习惯。护教军挡在了太空野狼的前进之路上，而太空野狼则毫不在意地猛力进攻，消灭了欧姆尼塞亚的战士们。情况变得越来越糟糕，奥普蒂孔22号不得不下达了最后的命令。

languages.text: Hélas, les deux escouades étaient bien incapables de s'adapter à leurs pratiques respectives. Les skitarii gênaient les anges de l'Empereur, qui en retour abattaient les guerriers de l'Omnimessie avec des attaques trop imprudentes. La victoire étant sur le point de leur échapper, Opticon-22 a pris la décision de lancer son tout dernier ordre.
languages.original_text: Alas, there was no understanding of each other's customs of combat. The Skitarii hindered the Emperor's Angels, and the latter destroyed the Omnissiah's warriors with careless attacks. Victory was slipping from their grasp, thus Opticon-22 issued his final order.

traits.locale_text: Hélas, les deux escouades étaient bien incapables de s'adapter à leurs pratiques respectives. Les skitarii passaient leur temps à gêner les anges de l'Empereur, qui en retour abattaient les guerriers de l'Omnimessie avec des attaques trop imprudentes. La victoire étant sur le point de leur échapper, Opticon-22 a pris la décision de lancer son tout dernier ordre.

languages.text: 残念なことに、ふたりは互いの戦闘習慣を理解できていなかった。スキタリは皇帝の天使の邪魔をし、皇帝の天使は不注意な攻撃で万機神の戦士たちを破壊していた。そのため、オプティコン-22は最後の命令を下した。
languages.original_text: Alas, there was no understanding of each other's customs of combat. The Skitarii hindered the Emperor's Angels, and the latter destroyed the Omnissiah's warriors with careless attacks. Victory was slipping from their grasp, thus Opticon-22 issued his final order.

languages.text: Lamentablemente, ninguno de los grupos comprendía las costumbres de combate del otro. Los Skitarii interferían en los ataques de los ángeles del Emperador, que a su vez masacraban a los guerreros del Omnissiah con ataques descuidados. La victoria se les escapaba de las manos cuando Opticon-22 dio su última orden.
languages.original_text: Alas, there was no understanding of each other's customs of combat. The Skitarii hindered the Emperor's Angels, and the latter destroyed the Omnissiah's warriors with careless attacks. Victory was slipping from their grasp, thus Opticon-22 issued his final order.

languages.text: Leider verstanden die beiden jedoch die Kampftraditionen des jeweils anderen nicht. Die Skitarii behinderten die Engel des Imperators, und diese wiederum zerstörten mit unbedachten Angriffen die Krieger des Omnissiah. Der Sieg war dabei, ihnen zu entgleiten, weshalb Opticon-22 seinen letzten Befehl erteilte.
